    "## Web Scraping Basics"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- [Building a Web Scraper from start to finish](https://hackernoon.com/building-a-web-scraper-from-start-to-finish-bb6b95388184)\n",
